_sText:
BIGGEST THX TO WINDOWS LIVE! FOR TESTING THIS MAP WITH ME <3


This is Version 2 of my beach he_ map.
Changelog:
FIXED:
-3D Skybox Water texture. Its now scaled down to fit the normal texture
-3D Skybox Water position. Now fits perfectly
ADDED:
-Many little plants to make it more Island-like
-trigger_hurt behind every house to prevent camping behind those! Does 4 hp damage each half a second!
CHANGED:
-Where the palms are. This map is no more symmetric!
-The Island is not a block anymore: it now is more rounded
-The Island is a bit bigger now

**UPDATE**
Now on version v2.2
FIXED: CT's werent hurt when ducking in the water
CHANGED: Height of trigger_hurt on net to prevent low gravity overjumping!
pls redownload!

Now the orginal description:

This is my second map! Its a HE_ map. You are playing on a island in the middle of the ocean. To get grenades you have to walk to the little stations located at the water. Its not allowed to touch the net/go past it/jump over it! Doing so will kill you!
Credits: nzero for the palm model
The rest is original stuff.
Have much fun!

Map made by Suicide Man 2oo7
